race.description: Ladbrokes Mega Multi Christmas Cup Handicap (C3)
race.comment: CAPITAL BOSS (3) got a long way back when fresh on the Poly at the Gold Coast, closing well over the 1540m trip. His trial coming in was good too and coming back to this level looks ideal. Maps beautifully from a good draw and can build on the first-up effort. INCA TRAIL (11) was outclassed at the Sunny Coast last start and will find this much easier than what he's been racing in recently. Right back to country grade now looks ideal and he has the early speed to roll across from the draw. Will take plenty of catching if he brings his recent form to this. LONDON POINT (6) disappointed last start following a good effort at Inverell two starts ago. That effort rates highly in this field and a return to that level can see her in the finish.
